
<p><em>Tsuki no Kaze (Wind of the Moon) ~Loran&#8217;s Day~</em> is a manga one-shot by Akiman published in the 03/2004 issue of <em>Gundam Ace</em>. It led into the proper manga serialization of <em>Wind of the Moon</em> (full scanlation <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://tsukinomayu.com/manga-scanlations/" target="_blank">here</a>). <em>~Loran&#8217;s Day~</em> was not included in the official <em>WotM</em> volume release, so this one-shot is new material. You can think of it as a prequel to a prequel. It features Loran, along with Dona and Hammett (Loran&#8217;s childhood friends from episode #40 of <em>Turn A Gundam</em>). </p>



